Package: internet-monitor
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${ruby:Depends}, ruby (>= 2.7), iputils-ping, systemd, asl3-asterisk
Recommends: network-manager
Description: Internet connectivity monitor for AllStarLink ASL3+ nodes
 A robust internet connectivity monitoring service designed specifically
 for AllStarLink mobile nodes. This service automatically detects internet
 connection status and provides local audio announcements to keep operators
 informed of connectivity changes.
 .
 Features:
  * Automatic monitoring with configurable check intervals
  * Comprehensive connectivity testing (ping and DNS)
  * Local audio announcements via AllStarLink
  * Automatic log rotation
  * Network recovery attempts
  * Systemd service integration
